{"word":"爱","detail":[{"title":"基本字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"● "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱"},{"type":"strong","content":"（愛）"},{"type":"span","content":"àiㄞˋ","class":["pinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 对人或事有深挚的感情：喜"},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"。"},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"慕。"},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"情。"},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"戴。"},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"抚。"},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"怜。"},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"恋。"},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"莫能助（虽同情并愿意帮助，但力量做不到）。友"},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"。挚"},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"。仁"},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"。厚"},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"。热"},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 喜好（"},{"type":"span","content":"hào","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":"）："},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"好（"},{"type":"span","content":"hào","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":"）。"},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"唱歌。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 容易：铁"},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"生锈。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 重视而加以保护："},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"护。"},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"惜。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 吝惜：“百姓皆以王为"},{"type":"span","content":"爱","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"也”。"}]]},{"title":"同义词、反义词","content":[]},{"title":"英文翻译","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"love, be fond of, like"}]]},{"title":"详细字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱"},{"type":"text","content":" 愛 "},{"type":"span","content":"ài","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}],[{"type":"span","content":"〈动词〉","class":["parts"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1)  (形声。从心,旡("},{"type":"span","content":"jì","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":")声。本义:亲爱;喜爱)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(2) 对人或事物有深厚真挚的感情"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"惠,爱也。——《尔雅》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"爱施者,仁之端也。——《说苑·说丛》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"君子自爱,仁之至也。——《法言》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"爱亲者不敢恶于人。——《孝经》。沈宏曰:“亲至结心为爱。”"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"爱共叔段,欲立之。——《左传·隐公元年》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"停车坐爱枫林晚,霜叶红于二月花。——杜牧《山行》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"父母之爱子也,则为之计深远。——《战国策》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"公夫人甚爱女。——明·崔铣《记王忠肃公翱三事》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"爱其子,择师而教之。——唐·韩愈《师说》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"非疏骨肉爱过客。——《韩非子·五蠹》。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(3) 又如:爱幸(喜爱宠幸);爱乐(喜爱);爱敬(亲爱恭敬;喜爱敬重);爱劳动;爱祖国;爱人民"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(4) 男女间有情"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"结发为夫妻,恩爱两不疑。——《古诗四首》之三,见《文选》卷二十九"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"孟尝君舍人有与君之夫人相爱者。——《战国策·齐策》。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(5) 又如:爱色(喜欢女色)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(6) 喜好"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"爱听古人节义事。——清·袁枚《祭妹文》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"晋陶渊明独爱菊。——宋·周敦颐《爱莲说》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"秦爱纷奢,人亦念其家。——杜牧《阿房宫赋》。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(7) 又如:爱玩(爱好玩赏。后用以指爱好的玩物或对游玩的喜好)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(8) 爱护"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"吴广素爱人。——《史记·陈涉世家》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"好自将爱,一年便健。——《三国志·方伎传》。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(9) 又如:爱人以德(按照道德标准去爱护帮助他人);爱物(爱护万物)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(10) 常常发生某种行为,容易发生某种变化。如:爱发脾气;爱下雨"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(11) 爱惜,珍惜"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"爱莫助之。——《礼记·表记》。注:“犹惜也。”"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"千金之子,不死于盗贼,何哉?其身之可爱,而盗贼不足以死也。——苏轼《留侯论》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"尔爱其羊,我爱其礼。——《论语·八佾》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"不爱死,义也。——柳宗元《驳复仇议》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"国事至此,予不得爱身。——宋·文天祥《指南录后序》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(12) 又如:爱身(爱惜生命,贪生怕死)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(13) 舍不得;吝惜"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"齐国虽褊小,吾何爱一牛。——《孟子·梁惠王上》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(14) 又"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"百姓皆以王为爱也。"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"是故甚爱必大费,多藏必厚亡。——《老子》四十四章"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"不爱珍器重宝肥饶之地。——汉·贾谊《过秦论》。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(15) 又如:爱吝(爱惜,吝啬)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(16) 贪"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"文臣不爱钱,武臣不惜死,天下平矣。——《宋史·岳飞传》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(17) 友爱"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"兄爱弟敬。——《左传·隐公三年》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(18) 怜悯、怜恤、同情"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"若爱重伤,则如勿伤;爱其二毛,则如服焉。——《左传·僖公二十二年》"}]]},{"title":"词性变化","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱"},{"type":"text","content":" 愛 "},{"type":"span","content":"ài","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}],[{"type":"span","content":"〈名词〉","class":["parts"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1)  惠;仁爱"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"古之遗爱也。——《左传·昭公二十年》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"爱多者则法不立,威寡者则下侵上。——《韩非子》。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(2)  又如:爱惠(仁慈恩惠)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(3)  尊称对方的女儿为“令爱”"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(4)  姓"}]]},{"title":"常用词组","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱不忍释"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àibùrěnshì","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"见“爱不释手”"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱不释手"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àibùshìshǒu","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"喜欢得舍不得放手"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱称"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àichēng","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"表示亲昵、喜爱的称呼"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"珍妮是珍的爱称"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱宠"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àichǒng","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"宠爱;喜爱"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"由于他会阿谀奉承,而受到了当时统治者的爱宠"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱答不理"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àidā-bùlǐ","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"不爱答理。喻对人冷漠,没礼貌"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"他怎么能爱答不理的"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱戴"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àidài","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"衷心拥护"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱抚"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àifǔ","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"疼爱护慰"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱国"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àiguó","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"热爱自己的国家"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"爱国忧民有古风"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱国主义"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àiguózhǔyì","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"对国家的爱或忠心的思想;爱国者的美德和行动"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱好"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àihào","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1)喜爱;具有浓厚兴趣并积极参加"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"爱好游泳"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"业余爱好"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"(2)〈方〉∶感情融洽;要好"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"乡里人都和她很爱好"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱河"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àihé","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"佛法说爱情如河流,人一沉溺即不能脱身,因以为喻"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱护"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àihù","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"喜欢并维护"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"爱护公物"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱克斯光"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àikèsīguāng","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"也称X射线、伦琴射线。是一种电磁波,有很强的穿透能力。广泛用于医疗和科技方面"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱怜"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àilián","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"喜爱;怜爱"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱恋"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àiliàn","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1)多指男女之间相爱而恋恋不舍"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"(2)感到深深地吸引"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"爱恋乡土"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"爱侣"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àilǚ","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"相爱的伴侣"}]]},{"title":"康熙字典","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"【卯集上】【心字部】愛 "}],[{"type":"text","content":"〔古文〕"},{"type":"span","content":"𤔤"},{"type":"span","content":"𢟪"},{"type":"span","content":"𢛭"},{"type":"text","content":"【唐韻】烏代切【集韻】【韻會】於代切【正韻】於蓋切，"},{"type":"span","content":"𠀤"},{"type":"text","content":"同"},{"type":"span","content":"㤅"},{"type":"text","content":"。仁之發也。从心旡聲。又親也，恩也，惠也，憐也，寵也，好樂也，吝惜也，慕也，隱也。　又【孝經·諫諍章疏】愛者，奉上之通稱。　又【諡法】嗇於賜與曰愛。　又姓。宋刺史愛申。　又叶烏胃切，音穢。【詩·小雅】心乎愛矣，遐不謂矣。【楚辭·九章】世溷濁莫吾知，人心不可謂兮。知死不可讓，願勿愛兮。【袁宏·名臣贊】滄海橫流，玉石同碎。達人兼善，廢已存愛。【謝瞻·答靈運詩】尋塗塗旣睽，卽理理已對。絲路有恆悲，矧乃所在愛。　小篆作"},{"type":"span","content":"㤅"},{"type":"text","content":"。"}]]},{"title":"说文解字","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"【卷五】【夊部】"},{"type":"span","content":"愛","class":["kszi"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"行皃。从夊"},{"type":"span","content":"㤅"},{"type":"text","content":"聲。烏代切"}]]},{"title":"字源演变","content":[]},{"title":"同音字","content":[]}],"traditional":"愛","type":"通用字、常用字","pinyin":["ài"],"radical":"爫","stroke":"六画","total_stroke":"十画","t_radical":"爪","t_stroke":"六画","t_total_stroke":"十画","stroke_order":"ノ丶丶ノ丶フ一ノフ丶","input_method":{"bopomofo":"BBKE","number":"20407","unicode":"U+7231","wubi":"EPDC"}}